{"tid":527323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙鳳禮苑停車場男子貨Van內燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-01-12T13:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T08:29:48.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4974e18e65bd741aa96e74e255c352d798d6e8c8","tid":527323,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T13:56:52.000Z","msg":"【21:40】事主送院後不治<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙鳳禮苑停車場，晚上8時許，一名中年男子於貨車車尾內燒炭，女友到場揭發報案。警方及消防接報到場，將事主救出，送往廣華醫院搶救，惜抵院後不治。<br />\n據悉，事主因經濟問題而尋死。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180112/57700816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180112%2F57700816&d=KUovSg7Sk1ulPtZPieiY3qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e0a1f52e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180112%2F57700816&h=c8fce1c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180112/57700816</a>"},{"pid":"24e553b62cd2751c3340fe8a2127fbbac9ba2520","tid":527323,"uid":10692,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc63d9acdecc88e81e20291b35868c46d0a245be","tid":527323,"uid":22791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:27:39.000Z","msg":"賭"},{"pid":"49b1b9ee0b687a83090abe00b6c3d0377abcd2cb","tid":527323,"uid":165875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"突發"},{"pid":"46a204f2741fa748b70819b7b1cd64c428ce4ede","tid":527323,"uid":165875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多"}]}